# Local developer convenience scripts that operate on sibling repos.
# scripts/publish_ainl_native_pypi.sh is a thin wrapper around `maturin publish`
# for the `ainl_native` Rust crate. The crate itself lives in
# `sbhooley/ainl-cortex` (`ainl_native/Cargo.toml`) and the production publish
# path is its GitHub Actions release workflow (tag `ainl_native-v*`). This
# script is only the "publish a wheel from my Mac right now" path; it does not
# build, modify, or release anything in this repo, so it belongs alongside
# personal `.env`-style configuration rather than in the tracked tree.
scripts/publish_ainl_native_pypi.sh
